                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d180">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">723.2515/384: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-23T12:00:00-03:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 23, 1918, 12 noon.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received 3.57 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Statement of President handed to Da Gama the day Embassy received it. Before
                    receipt of message Minister had taken steps along line which your December 4th,
                    7 p.m. suggested.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morgan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
